  "body": "### Description\n\nBy default, the hibernate flushmode is set to AUTO.\r\nIt would be beneficial to have a quarkus property to set the hibernate flushmode to other flushmodes e.g. COMMIT in case you don't want the default flushmode. \r\n\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\nThe name of the property could be _quarkus.hibernate-orm.flushmode_.",
